okitem&amp;rft.btitle=Cig+ban+no+bar+burden+-+biz+up+despite+law&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Carl+Campanile&amp;rft.au=Carl+Campanile&amp;rft.date=2006-07-25&amp;rft.pub=New+York+Post&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fpqarchiver.nypost.com%2Fnypost%2Faccess%2F1083006201.html%3Fdids%3D1083006201%3A1083006201%26FMT%3DABS%26FMTS%3DABS%3AFT%26type%3Dcurrent%26date%3DJul%2B25%252C%2B2006%26author%3DCARL%2BCAMPANILE%26pub%3DNew%2BYork%2BPost%26edition%3D%26startpage%3D025%26desc%3DCIG%2BBAN%2BNO%2BBAR%2BBURDEN%2B-%2BBIZ%2BUP%2BDESPITE%2BLAW&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Smoking_ban"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
